      <p>Locution allows first-responders to receive alerts, respond to events, and log information for others.</p>
      <p>After our partner had produced a functional proof-of-concept, they asked Viget to improve the user experience. I led the interface design for this product, focusing on.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Feature Definition</strong> - Defining capablities that were not yet present in the proof-of-concept. </li>
        <li><strong>UX Design</strong> - Sketching, interaction design, prototyping, and final art production.</li>
