    <h2 class="chapter__title">Initial Assessment</h2>
    <div class="chapter__body">
      <p>Common with first iteration MVPs, the user interface had been assembled on-the-fly as features were developed. Once the core functionality had been proven, it was time to refactor those decisions into something efficient and easy-to-use. Key areas to improve were:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Multiple screens were fulfilling the same purpose</li>
          <li>The satellite map inhibited readability</li>
          <li>There was little visual prioritization</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

