    <h2 class="chapter__title">Main View</h2>
    <div class="chapter__body">
      <p>The main view consolidates two screens and allows a comprehensive view of all alerts in both map and list form.</p>
      <p>Rather than use a satellite map which obscures road names and introduces noise, I introduced a Mapbox theme that highlights pins, markers, and labels.</p>
